1. *Širom* svijeta ljudi su počeli da koriste internet. (People around the world have started to use the internet.)
2. Ona se razmešta *širom* zemlje. (She is distributed all over the country.)
3. *Širom* zemlje su se pojavili novi trendovi. (New trends have emerged all over the country.)
4. Ona je obišla *širom* svet. (She traveled around the world.)
5. *Širom* sveta se uvelo novo pravilo. (A new rule was introduced all over the world.)